  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/800330/extras/618a137c4d2a63c776b4f0b56ac55b71.webp?t=1564765565\" width=600 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Color Circle</strong></h2> <br><strong>Color Circle is a very addictive game where you must hit moving colored circles. </strong><br><br>Aiming is a big challenge when the target becomes smaller and faster, but you must destroy as much as you can. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/800330/extras/7de7bd5fdf802de30744be1f097adfc5.avif?t=1564765565\" width=600 height=330 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES :</strong></h2><br><strong>*Endless game mode with 100+ levels, you won’t get bored.</strong><br><br><strong>*100+ obstacles and combinations, creative and challenging.</strong><br><br><strong>*Cool effects, color and live animations.</strong><br><br>*Easy to play, hard to master.<br><br>*Steam Leaderboard<br><br>*Steam Achievements",
